      <div type="researchScenario" xml:id="sc_SSK_publishing3DObjects">
        <!-- It is possible to translate the prose, by duplicating the elements head, desc or term, and adding xml:lang attribute -->
        <head xml:lang="en" type="scenarioTitle">Webpublishing of 3D Objects in Nexus-Format</head>
        <desc type="definition" xml:lang="en">In order to make 3D Objects web accessible, they need to be both reduced in size
            as well as converted to a web accessible format. One of the toolsets providing this is the 3DHop presenter and
            the affiliated Nexus conversion and compression tool. This scenario describes the mandatory steps to prepare
            and publish 3D Objects using this toolset and the NXS multiresolution model.</desc>
